      "heading": "Connecting flights at another airport",
      "textPreview": "Connecting flights at another airportSometimes your trip may involve arriving at one New York airport and departing from another. For example, you might fly into LaGuardia (LGA) from St. Paul, Minnesota, and then depart from JFK on an international flight. If this applies to you:",
