      "id": "",
      "className": "chakra-stack css-sekf8j",
      "ariaLabel": "",
      "heading": "",
      "textPreview": "For traveling between JFK and EWR: Take the JFK AirTrain to Jamaica, transfer to LIRR to Penn Station, then transfer to NJ Transit to Newark Airport Rail Station, and finally take the EWR AirTrain to the terminal. Alternatively: Take the JFK AirTrain to the subway (​ from Jamaica",
      "rect": {
        "x": 313.3,
        "y": 1200,
        "w": 382.7,
        "h": 720
      },
      "styles": {
        "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
        "color": "rgb(9, 9, 11)",
        "fontFamily": "Helvetica Now for PANYNJ",
        "fontSize": "16px",
