      "id": "",
      "className": "chakra-stack css-sekf8j",
      "ariaLabel": "",
      "heading": "",
      "textPreview": "You can pre-arrange transportation between airports with a shuttle service, which may be best if you are traveling with a group or have oversized or large quantities of luggage. Shuttles between JFK and LGA Estimated travel time: 30-60 minutes Shuttles between JFK and EWR Estimat",
